+```
+
+**Key components:**
+- **EventBus** вҖ” sole communication mechanism between domain services and notifications
+- **NotificationService** вҖ” subscribes to 4 events (`order:created`, `order:status-changed`, `user:created`, `user:updated`), builds payloads, dispatches to adapters with FIFO ordering
+- **3 Adapters** (email, SMS, webhook) вҖ” pluggable transport, retry logic, never-throw contract
+- **PreferencesService** вҖ” per-user, per-channel opt-out gating (`emailEnabled`, `smsEnabled`, `webhookEnabled` + category subscriptions)
+- **NotificationHistoryService** вҖ” logs every notification to a queryable repository with delivery status tracking
+- **Validators** вҖ” pure functions for order status transitions and notification preference checks
+
+**Known limitations:**
+- `in-app` channel declared but no adapter implemented
+- `emailFrequency` field stored but not enforced (no batching infrastructure)
+- All event handlers produce email-channel notifications only; SMS/webhook dispatch requires calling `sendNotification` directly or extending handlers
+- Phone number storage not in preferences model (SMS recipients come from the payload)
+
+### Files modified
+- `src/services/notification.service.ts` (added user event handlers)
+- `tests/services/notification.service.test.ts` (added 2 tests)
+
+### Test status
+All 240 tests pass (238 existing + 2 new). Zero compilation errors. Zero TODO/FIXME comments.
